        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Pilot Act of 2018</b></p> <p> This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to allow student loan borrowers to defer their student loan debt while they obtain aeronautical experience required for airline transport pilot certificates.<br> </p>]]></text>
